    <item>
      <title>印度储备银行行长达斯表示，通胀必须降至 4% 才能降息</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-20/rbi-governor-das-says-inflation-must-slow-to-4-for-a-rate-cut</link>
      <description><![CDATA[印度储备银行行长沙克提坎塔·达斯表示，印度的通胀率必须显示出可持续地稳定在央行 4% 目标附近的迹象，然后才会考虑降息。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-20/rbi-governor-das-says-inflation-must-slow-to-4-for-a-rate-cut</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 20 Aug 2024 13:56:05 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>哈里斯哄抬价格计划将产生什么效果？</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-08-20/what-would-the-harris-price-gouging-plan-do-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[副总统卡马拉·哈里斯的经济顾问迈克·派尔谈到了她提出的打击哄抬物价的计划。派尔表示，该计划将重点关注食品和杂货行业、紧急情况以及现有州法律。他正在接受“彭博监视”节目的采访。（来源：彭博社）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-08-20/what-would-the-harris-price-gouging-plan-do-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 20 Aug 2024 13:52:18 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>巴西雷亚尔走弱，因央行行长对加息表示怀疑</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-20/brazil-real-weakens-as-central-banker-casts-doubt-on-rate-hike</link>
      <description><![CDATA[巴西央行行长罗伯托·坎波斯·内托表示，虽然正在考虑加息，但由于国际前景改善且预期未来几个月通胀将会放缓，加息的可能性低于市场目前的预测，随后，巴西雷亚尔走弱。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-20/brazil-real-weakens-as-central-banker-casts-doubt-on-rate-hike</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 20 Aug 2024 13:42:32 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>米歇尔称，每个人都想进入债券市场</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-08-20/everyone-wants-in-on-the-bond-market-michele-says-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[摩根大通资产管理公司全球固定收益主管鲍勃·米歇尔 (Bob Michele) 表示，每个人都想进入债券市场。他参加了“彭博监视”节目。（来源：彭博社）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-08-20/everyone-wants-in-on-the-bond-market-michele-says-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 20 Aug 2024 13:32:21 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
