    <item>
      <title>华尔街将仔细研究美联储会议纪要，寻找缩表结束的线索</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-20/wall-street-will-scour-fed-minutes-for-clues-on-the-end-of-qt</link>
      <description><![CDATA[随着华尔街对美联储何时完成当前量化紧缩政策的争论愈演愈烈，策略师们正在寻求美联储周三公布最新政策会议纪要时获得更多指引。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-20/wall-street-will-scour-fed-minutes-for-clues-on-the-end-of-qt</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 20 Aug 2024 13:30:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>亚马逊的人工智能支出计划阻碍其股价反弹</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-20/amazon-s-ai-spending-plans-keep-stock-from-joining-tech-rebound</link>
      <description><![CDATA[与其他大型科技股相比，亚马逊公司的大手笔支出是以牺牲利润为代价的，其股价也因此受到下跌。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-20/amazon-s-ai-spending-plans-keep-stock-from-joining-tech-rebound</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 20 Aug 2024 12:17:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>德国强劲的工资增长加剧了欧洲央行的通胀困境</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-20/germany-s-strong-wage-growth-adds-to-ecb-s-inflation-struggle</link>
      <description><![CDATA[德国央行表示，德国强劲的工资增长势头并未减弱，并可能使通胀维持高位——这对正在努力将价格涨幅恢复至 2% 目标的欧洲央行来说是一个令人担忧的信号。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-20/germany-s-strong-wage-growth-adds-to-ecb-s-inflation-struggle</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 20 Aug 2024 10:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>随着中国电动汽车调查的推进，欧盟计划对特斯拉汽车征收 9% 的关税</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-20/eu-plans-9-tariff-on-tesla-cars-as-china-ev-probe-advances</link>
      <description><![CDATA[欧盟周二表示，计划对从中国进口的特斯拉汽车征收额外 9% 的关税，同时欧盟已向汽车制造商通报了其决定草案，将对从中国进口的电动汽车征收最终关税。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-20/eu-plans-9-tariff-on-tesla-cars-as-china-ev-probe-advances</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 20 Aug 2024 10:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
